---
title: Easy Coconut Double Chicken Curry with Rice & Baby Broccoli
description: Rich, fragrant and bursting with warm spices, this easy coconut chicken curry is a beaming bowl of pure comfort! Served with
fluffy rice and tender greens, it’s a creamy, dreamy dish that’ll transport your taste buds straight to the tropics.
